Sydney Lewis

🍉 Bio

Hi! I’m a graduate student at Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health and I’m studying epidemiology with a focus on pharmacoepidemiology. I’m excited for future opportunities to learn more about drug development, safety, and utilization.

Outside of school, I love to run 👟, sew 🧵, and cook 🥗. I’m originally from Southern California and I’m having so much fun exploring Baltimore!
